Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:44.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬉しい楽しいばっかじゃない　自分次第
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.31,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ONCE MORE SMILE, TWICE MORE CHIME
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:49.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こっち向いてよダーリン
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:58.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}わたしの純愛に気づいて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:37.74,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}百分之多少的喜欢才算是恋爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:48.83,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怂是罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:52.55,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}头脑风暴滴滴答答 选一种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.01,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}云隙中一阵细雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:58.05,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不亚至高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:01.60,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少女心它阴晴不定 可爱且无敌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:04.14,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像杂乱无章的钟声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:11.40,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}百分之多少的喜欢才算是恋爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:15.11,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱着我直到我犯困吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:20.66,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像是科幻片般的白日梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:23.70,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亲吻我 打破剧中沉默吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:26.12,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}优柔寡断也好 抱紧我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.79,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}胸口闷得难受好难受好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:33.63,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心动无法预测
Comment: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:37.09,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's TRUE FOOL LOVE! Hold me tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:39.38,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鼓起勇气来呀 My darling
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:44.01,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不止于欢乐和欣喜 都取决于我们自己
Comment: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.31,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ONCE MORE SMILE, TWICE MORE CHIME
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:49.56,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}转过来看着我吧 Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:58.95,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}注意到我纯粹的爱呀
